	"data": "<div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَمَآ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> أَنفَقۡتُم مِّن نَّفَقَةٍ أَوۡ نَذَرۡتُم مِّن نَّذۡرٖ فَإِنَّ </div><div>ٱللَّهَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>يَعۡلَمُهُۥۗ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَمَا لِلظَّٰلِمِينَ مِنۡ أَنصَارٍ ٠٧٢ إِن </div><div>تُبۡدُواْ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلصَّدَقَٰتِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَنِعِمَّا هِيَۖ وَإِن تُخۡفُوهَا </div><div>وَتُؤۡتُوهَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱلۡفُقَرَآءَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَهُوَ خَيۡرٞ لَّكُمۡۚ وَيُكَفِّرُ عَنكُم </div><div>مِّن</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>سَيِّ‍َٔاتِكُمۡۗ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱللَّهُ بِمَا تَعۡمَلُونَ خَبِيرٞ ١٧٢ </div><div>۞لَّيۡسَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>عَلَيۡكَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> هُدَىٰهُمۡ وَلَٰكِنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَهۡدِي مَن يَشَآءُۗ </div><div>وَمَا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>تُنفِقُواْ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> مِنۡ خَيۡرٖ فَلِأَنفُسِكُمۡۚ وَمَا تُنفِقُونَ </div><div>إِلَّا</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>ٱبۡتِغَآءَ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَجۡهِ ٱللَّهِۚ وَمَا تُنفِقُواْ مِنۡ خَيۡرٖ يُوَفَّ </div><div>إِلَيۡكُمۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>وَأَنتُمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> لَا تُظۡلَمُونَ ٢٧٢ لِلۡفُقَرَآءِ ٱلَّذِينَ </div><div><a data-content='حبسهم الجهاد عن التصرف' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>أُحۡصِرُواْ</a></div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>فِي</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ لَا يَسۡتَطِيعُونَ <a data-content='ذهابا وسيرا للتكسّب' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ضَرۡبٗا</a> فِي </div><div>ٱلۡأَرۡضِ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>يَحۡسَبُهُمُ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> ٱلۡجَاهِلُ أَغۡنِيَآءَ مِنَ <a data-content='التّنزّه عن السؤال' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>ٱلتَّعَفُّفِ</a> </div><div>تَعۡرِفُهُم</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div><a data-content='بهيأتهم الدالّة على الفاقة والحاجة' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>بِسِيمَٰهُمۡ</a> لَا يَسۡ‍َٔلُونَ ٱلنَّاسَ </div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'><a data-content='إلحاحا في السّؤال' tabindex='0' role='button' class='fake-link tafsir' data-toggle='popover' data-placement='top'>إِلۡحَافٗاۗ</a> وَمَا تُنفِقُواْ </div><div>مِنۡ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>خَيۡرٖ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> فَإِنَّ ٱللَّهَ بِهِۦ عَلِيمٌ ٣٧٢ ٱلَّذِينَ يُنفِقُونَ </div><div>أَمۡوَٰلَهُم</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>بِٱلَّيۡلِ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَٱلنَّهَارِ سِرّٗا وَعَلَانِيَةٗ فَلَهُمۡ أَجۡرُهُمۡ </div><div>عِندَ</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'><div>رَبِّهِمۡ</div><div style='flex-grow:0.7'> وَلَا خَوۡفٌ عَلَيۡهِمۡ وَلَا هُمۡ يَحۡزَنُونَ </div><div>٤٧٢</div></div><div style='font-size:4.8vw; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-direction: row-reverse;'></div>",
